n=top align=left class=m><span class=title> To be a wizard?</span><hr size=1> Being that I am a wizard. (only a level 15) but i am twinked (yes earned all my stuff not begged) i have a crystalline robe,dagger of frost, etc etc. I have been wondering is it worth it? i only play like 5-10 hours a week and not sure if i should stick it out as a wizard. even at this level no one wants to group with me. i have defended my class for as long as i  have played it. (fairly long time, i like to talk to people  a lot) i like casters a lot, and  dont really like chanters, but have only played a necro and mage till level 5 and that is by no means learning the class. if i do switch classes, i will have to start major newb levels all over again ( i realize im not that high, but it is just annoying) and try to get rid of my dagger of frost, which is hard to get rid of, almost impossible at this point. suggestions would be very nice, and please if you wish to flame me, try to hold it in.<br>
