Elauriel Dragonstorm<br>
55th Level Evoker<br>
Innoruuk Server <p><img src ="http://www.guildmagic.com/pics/32282.jpg"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=artillis>Artillis</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/16/01 5:18:37 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: re:to be a wizard</span><hr size=1> If your main consern is group disirability you will have just as hard a time with a mage or necro in group disirability a little latter on in the game.  Early on they are disirable for there pets but latter in the game dependign on your server and the people they would rather have anouther tank over a mage.  Some people are weird.  For exp grinds mages do tend to be more sought after.  However when you hit the high end game Wizards are very very highly sought for raids.  Don't play a necro unless you love to solo, hardly anyone likes to group with necros. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><br><font color=#ffffff>- </font><a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation>Graffë's Wizard Discussion</a><font color=#ffffff> - </font><a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1>General Discussion</a> <font color=#ffffff> - </font><br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 6.3.5<br>Copyright ©1999-2001 ezboard, Inc.</center></body></html>  